Given the number of buns, check if they can be distributed among 4 people equally.
        If divisible by 4 → Print "NO" (not possible to give equal buns to all 4)
        If not divisible by 4 → Print "Yes" (possible to give some buns to each)

n=int(input("Enter the number of test cases:"))
for i in  range( 0,n):
   n1=int(input("Enter the number of buns:"))
   if n1%4==0:
      print("NO")
   else:
      print("Yes")


